
Ticket: <%= resource.subject.black.bold %>

<%= "ID: #{ resource._id }, external_id: #{ resource.external_id }, url: #{ resource.url }".light_blue %>

Properties:
-----------

Type: <%= resource.type %>
Description: <%= resource.description %>
Priority: <%= resource.priority %>
Status: <%= resource.status %>
Has incidents: <%= colorize_boolean(resource.has_incidents) %>
Via: <%= resource.via %>
Due at:  <%= resource.due_at %>


Meta:
-----

Created at: <%= resource.created_at %>
Tags:  <%= resource.tags.join(", ") %>


Submitter:
--------
<% if resource.submitter_id.nil? %>
Anonymous
<% elsif resource.submitter.nil? %>
Submitter #<%= resource.submitter_id %>
<% else %>
ID: <%= resource.submitter._id %>
Name: <%= resource.submitter.name %>
Email: <%= resource.submitter.email %>
<% end %>

Assigne:
--------
<% if resource.assignee_id.nil? %>
No user has been assigned to the ticket yet
<% elsif resource.assignee.nil? %>
Assignee #<%= resource.assignee_id %> [User does not exist anymore]
<% else %>
ID: <%= resource.assignee._id %>
Name: <%= resource.assignee.name %>
Email: <%= resource.assignee.email %>
<% end %>

Organization:
-------------
<% if resource.organization %>
ID: <%= resource.organization._id %>
Name: <%= resource.organization.name %>
<% else %>
No organization has been assigned to the ticket yet
<% end %>

<%= ("-" * 100).black.bold %>
